** move bottom bar to top?

add

position top

to the bar { ... } block of the config

** chrome stored passwords issue

need to autostart the gnome-keyring-daemon

exec --no-startup-id /usr/bin/gnome-keyring-daemon --start --components=secrets

need to call chrome with the following option:

--password-store=gnome

*alternate*.

This seems to make things nice:

exec --no-startup-id /usr/lib/gsd-xsettings


